channel.title: Project Zanaris - Just a small project (Name Changed)
channel.description:
Alright, i'll give you some background information on this project before i get into it other stuff. This server is Delta Based. I started this project a little while before Christmas 2012 and worked on it for about 1 month or so. I lost interest a little while after when I was visiting my friends in a different state and just started back up about 1 week ago so it may seem like i've not done much so far but i'll be updating this thread a lot. Thanks for looking!
My intentions for this server is to be a PK/Economy server, kind of like the days back when "WebsterScape" was big, it was and always will be my favorite server. I'm not really making this server to host, just to release one day for other people to use as i'm not a big fan of hosting after a few bad runs. [size=12pt]ANY SUGGESTIONS ARE WELCOME[/size]
Green = Done Blue = Working on Red = Not done yet
[b][u]Currently Done[/u][/b]
[ul][li]Added a lot of commands[/li] [li]Edited Teleports[/li] [li]New Home[/li] [li]Update: Edited teleporting interface (2/15/13)[/li] [li]Update: Finished editing teleports for now (2/16/13)[/li] [li]Update: Working on Skilling area (2/16/13)[/li] [li]Update: New Home + New server name (2/16/13)[/li] [li]Update: Edited ground/floor sprites and need opinions (2/17/13)[/li] [li]To be completely honest, i really haven't added anything big at all yet[/li][/ul]
[b][u]Coming Soon[/u][/b]
[ul][li]New Skilling Area[/li] [li]Working Castle Wars[/li] [li]Some Working Quest[/li] [li]More Customs[/li] [li]Some custom minigames[/li] [li]Much More![/li][/ul]
I will be adding pictures once i have something good to add and I will continuously be adding them till i am done with this project. If you are interested in joining me with this project PM me on here, otherwise thanks for reading!! Please no hate, i know it may not seem like a lot now but give me some time before you judge :D
[img]http://img803.imageshack.us/img803/3512/screenshot3tc.png[/img] [img]http://img560.imageshack.us/img560/1276/screenshot1jn.png[/img] [img]http://img203.imageshack.us/img203/6613/screenshot1ns.png[/img] [img]http://img812.imageshack.us/img812/6094/screenshot1fkv.png[/img] [img]http://imageshack.us/a/img16/8500/screenshot2rgl.png[/img] [img]http://imageshack.us/a/img40/7554/screenshot1ye.png[/img] [size=10pt]WE NEED OPINIONS ON THE LAST 2 IMAGES SO FEEL FREE TO SAY WHATEVER YOU WANT[/size]
